    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A peaceful land has been overtaken by the dark wizard Cormac. Countless horrors hunt and kill those who try to escape. It is up to Edward, the captain of the guard, to defeat Cormac and save the kingdom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your quest begins just outside the castle walls in the graveyard. The wizard waits for you at the tallest tower. Fight your way to the top of the castle and save the kingdom from Cormac!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231520/extras/878db123d53860db6b16f7fc796b2097.avif?t=1770746441\" width=616 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you climb to the top of the Keep, you’ll face zombies, vampires, and other creatures that lurk in the darkness. Use crossbows, shotguns, or even a rocket launcher to dispose of them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231520/extras/83df10e2bddc6f5045020115d584758d.avif?t=1770746441\" width=616 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Juliet, a sorceress loyal to the king (or maybe just a certain knight in armor) will assist Edward on his journey. She can upgrade your abilities and sell you items or even help you craft weapons!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231520/extras/01522ca0ae744ad3bba0d4a264ee5199.avif?t=1770746441\" width=616 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Bleakest Keep is a highly replayable game. Test your skills and earn ranks based on your performance. Challenge yourself by aiming for higher ranks and faster times as you climb the Keep and defeat Cormac! Completing some challenges will unlock new outfits for Edward and Juliet!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight through 4 dark fantasy themed levels!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 30 weapons ranging from bows to shotguns to even frying pans!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your abilities and increase your power!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slay swarms of zombies and other dark fantasy creatures!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Highly replayable! Earn ranks and set new record times! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete challenges and unlock outfits for Edward and Juliet!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlockable survival mode allowing you to play as Edward, Juliet, and 4 of the game's bosses!</p></li></ul>",
